GET      /topN/region-InfTopErr        controllers.DeviceController.getInfTopErr(id: String ?= "",month: String ?= "")
## tab Monthly-Compare
GET      /monthly/getCompare           controllers.DeviceController.compareByMonth(month: String ?= "")
## tab Monthly-Trending
